'''Merciless''' can refer to several things:
*'''''[[Merciless (Star Destroyer)|Merciless]]''''', an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]].
*'''''[[Merciless (EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate)|Merciless]]''''', an Imperial [[Frigate/Legends|frigate]] in operation during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].
*'''''[[Merciless (Aggressor-class)|Merciless]]''''', an [[Aggressor-class Star Destroyer|''Aggressor''-class Star Destroyer]] belonging to [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lord]] [[Tyber Zann]].
*'''[[Merciless (massiff)|Merciless]]''', the pet [[Massiff/Legends|massiff]] of [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Kedar Blackgate]].
*'''''[[Merciless Captivator]]''''', a freighter
